│                                                                                                                     │
│ Step 1: Calculate the number of days between LMP and today.                                                         │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ First, find the number of days from LMP to the end of October 2022:                                                 │
│ - October has 31 days. From October 1 to October 31 is 30 days (since October 1 is day 1, so days remaining: 31 - 1 │
│ = 30).                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ But we can calculate the total days by counting from LMP to today.                                                  │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ From October 1, 2022 to June 13, 2023:                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ - From October 1, 2022 to October 31, 2022: 30 days (as above)                                                      │
│ - November 2022: 30 days                                                                                            │
│ - December 2022: 31 days                                                                                            │
│ - January 2023: 31 days                                                                                             │
│ - February 2023: 28 days (2023 not leap year)                                                                       │
│ - March 2023: 31 days                                                                                               │
│ - April 2023: 30 days                                                                                               │
│ - May 2023: 31 days                                                                                                 │
│ - June 1 to June 13, 2023: 13 days                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ Now sum these:                                                                                                      │
│ October: 30                                                                                                         │
│ November: 30                                                                                                        │
│ December: 31                                                                                                        │
│ January: 31                                                                                                         │
│ February: 28                                                                                                        │
│ March: 31                                                                                                           │
│ April: 30                                                                                                           │
│ May: 31                                                                                                             │
│ June: 13                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ Total days = 30 + 30 = 60                                                                                           │
│ 60 + 31 = 91                                                                                                        │
│ 91 + 31 = 122                                                                                                       │
│ 122 + 28 = 150                                                                                                      │
│ 150 + 31 = 181                                                                                                      │
│ 181 + 30 = 211                                                                                                      │
│ 211 + 31 = 242                                                                                                      │
│ 242 + 13 = 255 days.                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ So, 255 days have passed since LMP.                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ Step 2: Convert days to gestational weeks and days.                                                                 │
│ Gestational age is typically calculated in weeks and days from LMP.                                                 │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ 1 week = 7 days                                                                                                     │
│ So, divide total days by 7 to get weeks and remainder days.                                                         │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ 255 ÷ 7 = 36 weeks and 3 days (since 7 * 36 = 252, and 255 - 252 = 3 days).                                         │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ Therefore, gestational age is 36 weeks and 3 days.                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                     │
│ Final answer:                                                                                                       │
│ ANSWER: (36, 3)   (meaning 36 weeks and 3 days)                                                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

